OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1779700299
OL,3,CHS2 boss says cost increase is
OL,4,C'terrible news'
OL,6,FHS2's boss has described the increase
OL,7,Fin the cost of the project as
OL,8,F"terrible news".
OL,10,FChief executive Mark Wild told MPs
OL,11,F"the budget's doubled in five years".
OL,13,FThe Government announced on Tuesday
OL,14,Fthat the expected cost of completing
OL,15,Fthe high-speed railway was between
OL,16,F#87.7 billion and #102.7 billion (in
OL,17,F2025 prices).
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@OO]sD@AOUsD@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
