OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1779700299
OL,3,CHS2 boss says cost increase is
OL,4,C'terrible news'
OL,6,FMr Wild told the Transport Select
OL,7,FCommittee on Wednesday: "Let's just
OL,8,Facknowledge this is terrible news, and
OL,9,Fwe have to really think about the
OL,10,Freasons for that."
OL,12,FWhen then-prime minister Boris Johnson
OL,13,Fgave HS2 the go-ahead in February
OL,14,F2020, the funding envelope for the
OL,15,Fline from London to Birmingham was set
OL,16,Fat #44.6 billion (in 2019 prices).
OL,18,FThe new target opening schedule for
OL,19,FHS2 is between May 2036 and October
OL,20,F2039.
OL,26,@oD@YOUrD@RO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1779700299
OL,3,CHS2 boss says cost increase is
OL,4,C'terrible news'
OL,6,FMr Wild said he is "very confident
OL,7,Fthat these bookends of time and cost
OL,8,Fare robust".
OL,10,FThe "reset" of HS2 which led to the
OL,11,Fupdated cost and schedule has "taken a
OL,12,Fwhole year" and he was given "the time
OL,13,Fand space to go through this job with
OL,14,Fa fine tooth comb", he said.
