OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1779700299
OL,3,CHS2 boss says cost increase is
OL,4,C'terrible news'
OL,6,FHe told the committee that after five
OL,7,Fyears of HS2 civil engineering, he
OL,8,Fknows "how much it costs to move a
OL,9,Fcubic metre of earth".
OL,11,FHe said prices have been checked
OL,12,Fagainst similar projects, plans for
OL,13,Ffuture work have been put into "the
OL,14,Fright sequence", and the cost and
OL,15,Fschedule ranges have been subjected to
OL,16,F"a very, very thorough assurance".
OL,18,FMr Wild, who began his role in
OL,19,FDecember 2024, added: "I'm not here to
OL,20,Fcriticise what was done in 2020. I
OL,21,Fwasn't here.
OL,26,@pD@GOUqD@UO]uD@`OUvD@OO]xD@AOUxD@aO]{D@
OL,26,AWOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1779700299
OL,3,CHS2 boss says cost increase is
OL,4,C'terrible news'
OL,6,F"What I do know is that these ranges
OL,7,Fhave been subject to the most detailed
OL,8,Fscrutiny from people who really know
OL,9,Fhow to build these projects.
OL,11,F"For those reasons I really do think
OL,12,Fthese are robust."
OL,14,FMr Wild said the "singular root cause"
OL,15,Fof the project's huge cost increase
OL,16,Fwas that work started onsite "with
OL,17,Fimmaturity of design".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUtD@RO]vD@ROUvD@fO]xD@^OUyD@
OL,26,AUO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
