OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1779700299
OL,3,CHS2 boss says cost increase is
OL,4,C'terrible news'
OL,6,FAsked about the need to use ranges to
OL,7,Festimate the cost and schedule, he
OL,8,Fsaid his previous role at Crossrail `
OL,9,Fbuilding the infrastructure used by
OL,10,FLondon's Elizabeth Line ` taught him
OL,11,F"best practice is to use a range" when
OL,12,Fdealing with "things in the future
OL,13,Fthat are uncertain".
OL,15,FHe added: "There is still a great deal
OL,16,Fof uncertainty in this programme."
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@aO]tD@NOUuD@SO]wD@KOUxD@bO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1779700299
OL,3,CHS2 boss says cost increase is
OL,4,C'terrible news'
OL,6,FHe said it is his objective to deliver
OL,7,Fthe project at "the front end of the
OL,8,Franges", but warned: "Mistakes
OL,9,Fprojects have made in the past,
OL,10,Fincluding Crossrail, was becoming
OL,11,Fhostage to fortune of unrealistic
OL,12,Fforward-leaning dates."
OL,14,FRail minister Lord Hendy told the
OL,15,Fcommittee: "Anybody listening to this
OL,16,Fwould be rightly horrified."
OL,26,@oD@POUpD@GO]pD@VOUtD@WO]wD@LOUxD@\O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
