OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1779700299
OL,3,CHS2 boss says cost increase is
OL,4,C'terrible news'
OL,6,FHe explained that when he started in
OL,7,Fhis role in July 2024, HS2 Ltd
OL,8,Fpresented him with figures for the
OL,9,Fprogress of the project which had "no
OL,10,Fsubstance".
OL,12,FHe added: "This is a disastrous place
OL,13,Fto be with the project at this stage."
OL,15,FHe said the Government is "confident"
OL,16,Fabout the process now in place, but
OL,17,F"you wouldn't half have liked this
OL,18,Fprocess to have started quite a long
OL,19,Ftime ago".
OL,26,@qD@cOUrD@JO]tD@KOUuD@fO]wD@[OUwD@eO]yD@
